article.headline: Robert Morris 55, Maine 43
article.story: ORONO, Maine (AP) -- A.J. Jackson had 21 points and 12 rebounds to help Robert Morris beat Maine 55-43 on Sunday. Tony Lee added 12 points for Robert Morris (4-0), which outscored Maine (2-4) 22-6 at the start of the second half to take a 48-32 lead. Jon Sheets led Maine with 13 points.
